<span id="freeTextContainer5865667263540066794">A brilliant book! Beverly does a fantastic job of showing how Leigh&apos;s writing changes as he keeps writing. At first it is short with little to say and by the end he is getting good at showing what happens. A simple story. This is similar to Crenshaw in several ways. This is a powerful story and I can&apos;t believe it took me this long to read it. There are great tips if children really want to be a writer too. Please get kids to read this. It&apos;s a story will enjoy.</span>
