<div id="review_3261690571" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3261690571" />
    <a title="Molly Titera" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9125753-molly-titera"><img alt="Molly Titera" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1444186440p2/9125753.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3261690571?book_show_action=true">Feb 22, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Molly Titera" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Molly Titera" href="/user/show/9125753-molly-titera">Molly Titera</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9125753-molly-titera?shelf=8-10-years-old">8-10-years-old</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3261690571" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3216421510056563574">This was a great read with the kids because it brought up topics and ideas that I was glad to discuss with the kids. It inspired them to write and write letters; record thoughts and ideas. Make yourself vulnerable in writing. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


